{"tid":530372,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【有埋rundown】如果衛蘭搞返個《OMJ冇唱到之演唱會》，質素應該拍得住OMJ","createTime":"2018-01-15T16:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T05:53:23.000Z","uid":165817,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a21cda36254096b1b24962dc38108a98544f58","tid":530372,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002933_8a84afac83970c3e05c0541da4e561bd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F002933_8a84afac83970c3e05c0541da4e561bd.JPG&h=aa1dd119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全部都係OMJ冇唱既歌，Rundown都諗埋，盡量跟返OMJ既編排，一樣係33首歌，一樣係五節加encore，每節中間俾蘭姨講下野換下衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盡量將容易令大家聯想起另一首歌既歌擺埋一齊，開頭係快歌同冧歌，之後中間係最受歡迎既苦情歌，每節都代表住天真小女孩去到真係認識戀愛既成長歷程同自我救贖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後enocre揀左兩首有氣氛既歌，同兩首蘭姨最鍾意既「Love」主題做結尾，類似OMJ天敵同就算世界無童話咁。排個好setlist原來好難，希望大家不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇rundown之前梗係睇下靚相先啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002933_4e0070870259d2f01b9c1c9b65e3e718.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F002933_4e0070870259d2f01b9c1c9b65e3e718.JPG&h=79229a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002935_dfa242202af4ab7832665e6c5d4cfa44.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F002935_dfa242202af4ab7832665e6c5d4cfa44.JPG&h=b462cc2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002934_1101268abd3a2207ffb73e739cc6325c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F002934_1101268abd3a2207ffb73e739cc6325c.JPG&h=c9c6ff77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 越幫越忙<br />\n2. My Cookie Can<br />\n3. 我愛呼吸<br />\n4. 深愛<br />\n5. 我們的故事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002934_f0068386dab09388c83a939fd62a3b74.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F002934_f0068386dab09388c83a939fd62a3b74.JPG&h=ba7fcdba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002935_8e19540167df4c7d121c59b3cb1aa4b3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F002935_8e19540167df4c7d121c59b3cb1aa4b3.JPG&h=155d6cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 2004<br />\n7. Pretty<br />\n8. 主角愛我<br />\n9. 夏日傾情<br />\n10. 24 (嘉賓：應昌佑)<br />\n11. 童夢 (嘉賓：應昌佑)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002935_d0ee874f8d2919e12cae69ae02cb1edd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F002935_d0ee874f8d2919e12cae69ae02cb1edd.JPG&h=90830145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002936_1efa4ad7d88ded6b2a6a3f4ff74bd511.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F002936_1efa4ad7d88ded6b2a6a3f4ff74bd511.jpeg&h=a4117aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12. 退<br />\n13. 如水<br />\n14. 積雪<br />\n15. 溫差<br />\n16. 你的女人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002936_6dde8e749290cceadab749c2cad25bd6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F002936_6dde8e749290cceadab749c2cad25bd6.JPG&h=7f2b3f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/002936_57973ccb4dd5ed4c08947b6ee25f0cfb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim